          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕的是天明亮难以回程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业、四鬼卒同下。家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "方才老元戎前来托梦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "醒来时不由人珠泪满胸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣孟二爷进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟二爷进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟良上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不听皇王诏宣，但听杨家令传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟少礼，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。唤末将进帐，有何军情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟有所不知，昨晚三更，偶得一梦，只见我父托兆与我，言道前番盗骨，乃"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是假的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真的呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真骸骨现在北国洪羊洞，望乡台第三层，那才是真。我有意，命贤弟二下番营"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去盗骨，不知贤弟意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "末将好比元帅跨下之驹，扬鞭就走，停鞭即止，但听元帅传令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，如此贤弟听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我命贤弟下北番，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此去哪怕路途难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿盗得尸骨转，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凌烟阁上美名传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，好一个凌烟阁上美名传，小心了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭、孟良同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
