    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "家院",
        "杨延昭",
        "老军"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孟良盗骨无音信，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院领老军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯！胆大小番，见了本帅，为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去掉盒儿，方可下跪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，将盒儿去掉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院取盒交杨延昭看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令公骸骨，啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见骸骨不由人泪双流，"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人与元帅叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你叫什么名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人名叫程宣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程宣，你奉何人所差？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉孟二爷所差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何为证？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有板斧为证。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将板斧收下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程宣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你孟二爷他往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦喝元帅！孟二爷前去盗骨，焦二爷暗地跟随，孟二爷一时失手，将焦二爷劈"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听罢言来泪双淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程宣，那孟二爷将焦二爷劈死，他因何不来见我啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦喝、元帅！孟二爷将焦二爷劈死，无有脸面来见元帅，他也自刎在洪羊洞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自刎在洪羊洞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟良！焦赞！啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说二将双双丧命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "失了我左右膀难以飞行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "老军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（老军下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "霎时间腹内痛心血上涌，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭、家院同下。）"
        }
      ],
